00:23:42,734 --> 00:23:44,432
der tsveyter bruder

461
00:23:44,432 --> 00:23:46,328
vos iz geven khasene gehat

462
00:23:45,734 --> 00:23:46,791
Yosef.

463
00:23:46,791 --> 00:23:47,470
Berl.

464
00:23:47,470 --> 00:23:48,724
ah, Berl, yo.

465
00:23:48,187 --> 00:23:50,187
Berl. hot er gelebt

466
00:23:50,187 --> 00:23:52,074
nit vayt fun Yurbrik.

467
00:23:52,074 --> 00:23:53,715
a sh- oykh a shtetl

468
00:23:53,715 --> 00:23:56,752
lebn, in Lite.

469
00:23:56,752 --> 00:23:57,696
dos iz oykh

470
00:23:57,696 --> 00:24:03,545
nit vayt arum Nemen, in Lite geven a taykh, a Nemen hot er geheysn.

471
00:24:03,545 --> 00:24:08,866
er hot dortn gelebt; er hot gehat a froy un er hot shoyn gehat a yingele a faynem.

472
00:24:08,866 --> 00:24:11,885
ah, iz,

473
00:24:11,885 --> 00:24:17,809
 ye, ⟨vos hob ikh gevelt zogn?⟩ ye,ho- hobn zey genum-, azoy, iz dokh geven in shtub iz geblibn nor

474
00:24:17,809 --> 00:24:19,621
di mame un der tate

475
00:24:19,621 --> 00:24:22,470
un di shvester, di Khaye

476
00:24:22,470 --> 00:24:24,149
un der bruder

477
00:24:24,149 --> 00:24:27,791
ho- hot gelebt mit di froy, bazunder.

478
00:24:27,791 --> 00:24:31,583
do hot men genumen mener oyf der arbet.

479
00:24:31,583 --> 00:24:35,508
mener hot men genumen oyf der arbet, un m'hot genumen mayn bruder.

480
00:24:35,508 --> 00:24:41,093
un mayn shvester, az zi hot gekent ale poyerim dortn UNK az me ken zikh eyner dem tsveytn.

481
00:24:41,093 --> 00:24:43,394
zogt zi tsum poyer

482
00:24:43,394 --> 00:24:49,735
zogt zi "vos nemstu im? du zest dokh az er ge-, er iz kra- er hinkt un er geyt mit a shtekn. nem im nit."

483
00:24:49,735 --> 00:24:52,074
az er git ir a shlep

484
00:24:52,074 --> 00:24:53,564
zogt er azoy:

485
00:24:53,564 --> 00:24:56,508
"oyber du, er ken nit geyn, iz kum.

486
00:24:56,508 --> 00:24:58,451
vestu im hitn."

487
00:24:58,451 --> 00:25:01,753
un er hot ir shoyn nit opgelozn.

488
00:25:01,753 --> 00:25:04,772
iz zi avek di shvester mit di mener

489
00:25:04,772 --> 00:25:07,904
geblibn iz mayn mame eyner aleyn.

490
00:25:07,904 --> 00:25:11,621
mayn mame iz geven letstns zeyer a kranke froy.

491
00:25:11,621 --> 00:25:14,489
a shvakhe un a kranke.

492
00:25:14,489 --> 00:25:16,942
flegt zi loyfn bay di shvegerin

493
00:25:16,942 --> 00:25:19,413
bay di shnur UNK kumen di mame's

494
00:25:19,413 --> 00:25:22,413
bay Libe'n, flegt zi dortn zayn.

495
00:25:22,413 --> 00:25:24,300
un eyner aleyn.

496
00:25:24,300 --> 00:25:26,153
un der tate vos iz geven?

497
00:25:25,658 --> 00:25:29,696
der tate iz avek m- oyf der arbet, hot men genumen ale mener.

498
00:25:29,696 --> 00:25:32,828
iz der tate avek un der bruder avek

499
00:25:32,828 --> 00:25:36,790
un m'hot tsugenumen di shvester, ye.

500
00:25:36,790 --> 00:25:39,469
zey avekgefirt oyf der arbet

501
00:25:39,469 --> 00:25:41,620
un di mame iz gegangen tsu di shnurn.

502
00:25:41,620 --> 00:25:45,695
un di mame flegt geyn tsu di sh- a gantsn tog flegt zi zayn tsu di shnur

503
00:25:45,695 --> 00:25:48,903
un bay nakht flegt zi kumen in shtub shlofn.

504
00:25:48,903 --> 00:25:51,846
PITOM hot men UNK genumen

505
00:25:51,846 --> 00:25:53,884
di vayber oykh.

506
00:25:53,884 --> 00:25:56,601
hot men tsuzamengenumen ale froyen

507
00:25:56,601 --> 00:26:01,412
vayl s'iz geblibn nor di froyen; di mener hot men frier tsuzamengenumen.

508
00:26:01,412 --> 00:26:04,865
hot men genumen di froyen; azoy di mener

509
00:26:04,865 --> 00:26:09,205
hot men tsuzamengenumen. m'hot zey gefirt a por teg oyf der arbet

510
00:26:09,205 --> 00:26:13,449
un ⟨m'hot zey⟩ avekgefirt, un dort iz geven a shtetl Sharki.

511
00:26:13,449 --> 00:26:16,770
oykh in Lite; dos iz geven nit vayt fun Kruki.

512
00:26:16,770 --> 00:26:23,355
m'hot zey dortn avekgefirt, un m'hot zey alemen dortn oysgeshosn.

513
00:26:23,355 --> 00:26:27,883
di sh- di glavne shisers zaynen geven di litviner.

514
00:26:27,883 --> 00:26:30,732
zey zaynen geven di glavne shisers.

515
00:26:30,732 --> 00:26:32,770
der daytsh hot geheysn

516
00:26:32,770 --> 00:26:35,996
un zey zaynen geven di glavne shisers.

517
00:26:35,996 --> 00:26:38,260
un di b- un di mamen

518
00:26:38,260 --> 00:26:40,335
mit di ale froyen

519
00:26:40,335 --> 00:26:44,958
iz in a bisl tsayt arum, ikh veys nit tsi oyf vifl vokhn, tsi vos

520
00:26:44,958 --> 00:26:48,071
hot men tsuzamgenumen ale froyen.

521
00:26:48,071 --> 00:26:51,958
m'hot avekgefirt, iz geven nokh a shtetl, Sapizhishok.

522
00:26:51,958 --> 00:26:55,109
dos iz geven nenter tsu Kovne. shoyn.

523
00:26:55,109 --> 00:26:57,920
un m'hot zey dortn alemen

524
00:26:57,920 --> 00:27:01,071
umgebrakht, ye.

525
00:27:01,071 --> 00:27:04,052
ot vel ikh dertseyln fun a litvin:

526
00:27:04,052 --> 00:27:05,052
dos iz UNK

527
00:27:04,510 --> 00:27:07,882
dos iz ge- SLIKHA, dos iz geven in eyn un fertsikster yor?

528
00:27:07,882 --> 00:27:10,033
in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

529
00:27:10,033 --> 00:27:10,877
vayter.

530
00:27:10,429 --> 00:27:11,867
vi di milkhome iz oysgebrokhn.

531
00:27:12,165 --> 00:27:14,750
dem alts in dem yor.

532
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:15,920
az s'hot oys-

533
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:20,448
vi s'hot oysge⟨brokhn⟩ iz di ershte teg hot men nit gekent aroysgeyn.

534
00:27:20,448 --> 00:27:22,165
ye.

535
00:27:22,165 --> 00:27:25,674
vu di, un di di shvester

536
00:27:25,674 --> 00:27:27,825
iz dokh geven mit tsvey kinder

537
00:27:27,825 --> 00:27:30,127
iz an UNK me darf dokh esn

538
00:27:30,127 --> 00:27:31,816
shoyn nito vos tsum esn

539
00:27:31,315 --> 00:27:33,259
yetst dertseylstu fun Kovne, yo?

540
00:27:33,259 --> 00:27:35,372
dos iz fun Kovne, in Kovne geven, ye.

541
00:27:35,372 --> 00:27:37,315
vi s'hot oysgebrokhn in Kovne di krig

542
00:27:37,315 --> 00:27:42,334
er, az du bist geven in Kovne mit di shvester, ir hot gevust vos tut zikh in Kruki?

543
00:27:42,334 --> 00:27:44,108
az m'hot avekgenumen ale

544
00:27:44,108 --> 00:27:44,881
neyn,

545
00:27:44,881 --> 00:27:46,091
mir hobn mit gevust.

546
00:27:45,257 --> 00:27:46,642
biz shpeter es iz

547
00:27:46,224 --> 00:27:48,749
nor ven, ven hob ikh zikh dervust

548
00:27:48,749 --> 00:27:52,995
vayl eyne iz gekumen, dos iz geven az mir zaynen geven in geto

549
00:27:52,995 --> 00:27:56,296
az mir zaynen geven in geto iz gekumen eyne

550
00:27:56,296 --> 00:27:58,484
di mame's a shokhnte

551
00:27:58,484 --> 00:28:01,824
un zi hot oyfgezukht undz in geto

552
00:28:01,824 --> 00:28:03,598
un zi iz geven bay undz

553
00:28:03,598 --> 00:28:06,673
un zi hot dos undz alts dertseylt.

554
00:28:06,673 --> 00:28:08,654
ye. nokh

555
00:28:08,654 --> 00:28:11,900
nu, do, glaykh vi s'hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome

556
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:14,975
dos iz geven in Kovne, iz

557
00:28:14,975 --> 00:28:19,107
hot shoyn, me darf zikh, hobn vos tsum, iz es, hot men gezogt

558
00:28:19,107 --> 00:28:22,339
az vu mayn shvester hot gelebt az antkegn

559
00:28:22,339 --> 00:28:24,735
ibern veg, iz geven

560
00:28:24,735 --> 00:28:28,301
ahm, ah, a krom fun

561
00:28:28,301 --> 00:28:30,640
broyt, khale

562
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:32,395
fun di zakhn.

563
00:28:32,395 --> 00:28:35,112
az m'git a khale

564
00:28:35,112 --> 00:28:38,527
g- az me shteyt in, in ⟨TOR⟩, in otshered

565
00:28:38,527 --> 00:28:40,565
un, in rey heyst es,

566
00:28:40,565 --> 00:28:43,414
git men yedn eynem a khale.

567
00:28:43,414 --> 00:28:47,282
bin ikh avekgegangen, un ikh hob zikh oykh geshtelt in rey

568
00:28:47,282 --> 00:28:49,320
ikh hob zikh azoy tsuzamengedreyt

569
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:51,942
un di tsure tsum vant az me zol mir nit

570
00:28:51,942 --> 00:28:54,885
me zol nit zen az ikh bin a yidishe

571
00:28:54,885 --> 00:28:56,583
un

572
00:28:56,583 --> 00:28:59,262
un do, ge- shteyendik azoy

573
00:28:59,262 --> 00:29:00,753
her ikh

574
00:29:00,753 --> 00:29:04,017
az s'kumt, geyt tsu a a litovets

575
00:29:04,017 --> 00:29:06,583
far mayne oygn shteyt er mir nokh ersht

576
00:29:06,583 --> 00:29:08,055
a hoykher

577
00:29:08,055 --> 00:29:11,527
mit a biks in hant; makht er azoy:

578
00:29:11,527 --> 00:29:14,998
"ikh," zogt er, "hob nekhtn" zogt er, "oysgeshosn

579
00:29:14,998 --> 00:29:16,564
SIMTU ZYDU"

580
00:29:16,564 --> 00:29:21,830
hundert yidn hot er oysgeshosn in Aleksot. ye.

